WEBVTT

00:14:26.083 --> 00:14:30.976
Well, I want to tell all of you
that she didn't give me a vaccine,

00:14:31.000 --> 00:14:33.059
because she loves me

00:14:33.083 --> 00:14:37.934
and because she believed
that that was the best thing for me.

00:14:37.958 --> 00:14:39.393
I think differently

00:14:39.417 --> 00:14:42.143
and I will never change her mind,

00:14:42.167 --> 00:14:44.083
but she's not a bad person."

00:14:45.292 --> 00:14:48.476
That was the message from a teenager.

00:14:48.500 --> 00:14:52.000
Empathy, kindness and understanding.

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:56.518
We have an abundance
of scientific information

00:14:56.542 --> 00:14:59.476
to debunk false rumors.

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:01.601
That's not our problem.